name: Dungeon Tail
description:
Enjoy a lewd dungeon romp through the Enchanted Caverns with Iris the bunny mage and Vyncent the wolf rogue, students of the prestigious Dungeon Delver Academy. Who knows what sorts of misadventures they'll run into~

The game is a visual novel featuring various branching paths and puzzles/mini-games. Of course, there are plenty of detailed lewd scenes and animations to discover and enjoy as well!
